{
  "texts": [
    "The final model performance assessment for each cycle was done on 179 separate independent test data, not in either training pool.",
    "We used FAO and SURFSARA cloud computing platforms 37, 43 to run inference of the fifteen land-use following deforestation classes across the entire African continent, 30 • south, 30 • north 22.",
    "The inference was run on 5 m resolution freely available planet-NICFI imagery using the attention U-Net model trained in Sect.",
    "\"Models and implementation details\".",
    "We used planet-NICFI imagery for the year 2022 as a proxy for predicting land-use following deforestation from the year 2000 to 2020."
  ]
}